al, from vintage how-to manuals to magazine articles for working photographers, this full-color book illustrates the evolution of trends with hundreds of pictures made by amateurs, artists, and commercial photographers alike. Whether for selfies or sepia tones, the rules for good pictures are always shifting, reflecting new ways of thinking about ourselves and our place in the visual world.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 26. Mai 2021) 0aAesthetics. 0aPhotographyxPhilosophy. 0aPhotographyxSocial aspectsxHistory. 7aPhotography / History.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertArt and Architecture eBook-Package 2020z978311073823008iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Arts 2020z9783110704655oZDB-23-DPK08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Arts, Architecture and Design 2020 Englishz978311070478508iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2020 Englishz978311070471608iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2020z9783110704518oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertSUP Frontlist eBook-Package 2020z978311069218140uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978150361232740uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781503612327423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9781503612327.jpg  a978-3-11-069218-1  SUP Frontlist eBook-Package 2020b2020  a978-3-11-070471-6  EBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2020 Englishb2020  a978-3-11-070478-5  EBOOK PACKAGE Arts, Architecture and Design 2020 Englishb2020  a978-3-11-073823-0  Art and Architecture eBook-Package 2020b2020  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aZDB-23-DGGb2020  aZDB-23-DPKb2020